high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the side of the wooden coffee table closest to the couch.
Pick up the closest watch off of the coffee table.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right again and walk up to the pink chair.
Put the watch into the cardboard box that is on the seat of the chair.
Pick up the cardboard box with the watch inside of it.
Turn right and walk back over to the coffee table.
Place the cardboard box with the watch inside of it onto the coffee table to the right of the set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a watch inside of it on the coffee table.

high_descs: turn to the left, make a left at the pink coach and move forward to the coffee table on the left and face the coffee table
pick up the watch on the front edge of the table
turn around and face the pink chair with a white box sitting on it
put the watch inside of the white box
pick up the white box with the watch inside of it
turn to the right and move to face the coffee table on the right
put the white box with the watch inside on the coffee table to the right of the set of keys
anns.task_desc: put a box with a watch inside on the coffee table

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the pink couch, turn to the coffee table.
Pick up the watch closest to the edge of the coffee table.
Walk to the pink chair.
Put the watch in the box on the chair.
Pick up the box from the chair.
Walk to the couch, turn to the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the box with the watch on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the coffee table.
Pick up wrist watch from the coffee table.
Walk toward the red chair and stand in front of it.
Put the watch in the box sitting on the red chair.
Pick up the box from the chair.
Turn right and walk back to the coffee table.
Set the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the watch in a box on the coffee table.

high_descs: While facing the small black table against the wall, turn and walk towards the door, hang a left and walk to the long side of the coffee table nearest the pink couch.
Pick up the wrist watch on the side of the table that is closest to the couch.
Turn towards your right and walk to the pink chair with a box on it at the left of the couch as you are facing the couch.
Place the watch in the back right corner of the box.
Pick up the box from the chair.
Turn and walk to the long side of the coffee table nearest the pink couch.
Place the box on the table to the right of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Put a wrist watch in a box, place the box on the coffee table
